1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image classification and face recognition. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of sparse representations and priors for classification. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems for image classification. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with multi-view face recognition. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of spike-and-slab priors, which are commonly used in neural networks.
